{"parentUuid":"664614f8-60a3-4a32-8e35-ffa4cf84a222","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"d273fc38-951b-436c-8df6-efe14ae0a8c3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"course section topic という階層でデータを持っています\ncourse -> section は１対多\nsection -> topic は１対多です\n\nSELECT する際に各小要素は配列の JSON　として 1クエリで取得したいんですがどうすればいいですか？ postgres です"},"uuid":"ffbd0e22-3d90-4186-994c-434078308d99","timestamp":"2026-03-28T21:05:04.587Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"22011a1c-862e-4622-850d-6b3a49d4b237","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"enrollment"}
{"parentUuid":"ffbd0e22-3d90-4186-994c-434078308d99","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01CyghJCzkB3jGzmVv8b927u","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30426,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30426},"output_tokens":49,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZWA6AjEwJ16Z1jwp7w81","type":"assistant","uuid":"6888a1ec-ab25-458a-b60a-259ef6ec11fc","timestamp":"2026-03-28T21:05:11.742Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"22011a1c-862e-4622-850d-6b3a49d4b237","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"enrollment"}
{"parentUuid":"6888a1ec-ab25-458a-b60a-259ef6ec11fc","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01CyghJCzkB3jGzmVv8b927u","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PostgreSQL で nested JSON 配列を取得するには、**`json_agg()` と `json_build_object()` のネスト**を使うのが標準的です。\n\n基本的なパターン：\n\n```sql\nSELECT \n  c.id,\n  c.name,\n  json_agg(\n    json_build_object(\n      'id', s.id,\n      'name', s.name,\n      'topics', COALESCE((\n        SELECT json_agg(json_build_object(\n          'id', t.id,\n          'name', t.name\n        ))\n        FROM topic t\n        WHERE t.section_id = s.id\n      ), '[]'::json)\n    )\n  ) as sections\nFROM course c\nLEFT JOIN section s ON c.id = s.course_id\nGROUP BY c.id, c.name;\n```\n\n**結果のイメージ：**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"数学\",\n  \"sections\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 101,\n      \"name\": \"第1章\",\n      \"topics\": [\n        {\"id\": 1001, \"name\": \"微分\"},\n        {\"id\": 1002, \"name\": \"積分\"}\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**ポイント：**\n- **サブクエリを使う** - JOINだと topic が重複行を作るため、各 section のサブクエリで取得する方が効率的\n- **COALESCE で空配列対応** - section に topic がない場合は `[]` を返す\n- **GROUP BY course** - course レベルで集約\n\n実際のテーブル構造を見れば、より最適化したクエリが書けます。今使ってるテーブル定義やカラム名があれば教えていただければ、実際のクエリを調整できます。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30426,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":1171,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30426,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZWA6AjEwJ16Z1jwp7w81","type":"assistant","uuid":"3f9dadac-e722-4628-aaf3-c569e625f602","timestamp":"2026-03-28T21:05:15.011Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"22011a1c-862e-4622-850d-6b3a49d4b237","version":"2.1.84